## üõ†Ô∏è Advanced

* **Custom v2ray path**:

  ```python
  app = CLIApp(db_path="mydb.json", v2ray_binary="C:\\v2ray\\v2ray.exe")
  ```
* **Force‚Äêarchive with ID collision**:

  ```python
  mgr.move_config("srv1", arc_mgr, force=True)
  ```
* **Speed testing**:
  Downloads 1 MiB over SOCKS5 using `requests[socks]`.

